description: The two new members of the House of Keys will hold the seats until next year's general election.
title: Douglas South: House of Keys by-election results declared
title_page: Douglas South: House of Keys by-election results declared - BBC News
maintext: He said, as the term was only for a year he could not make "any promises for the grander stage" but would work to improve issues in the local area, including bus services.
